{[#]White is better developed and seems to have pressure all over the board.
Is there a way out of the trouble for Black?} 16... Nc6 $1 {[%cal Gc6d4] When
underdeveloped, one should develop! And the last move is the best way to do it
as it attacks the dangerous d4-bishop.} (16... Nxc5 17. Rxe8+ Qxe8 18. Bxc5 Nc6
19. Rxd5 $16) (16... Na6 17. Nxe4 dxe4 18. Qg3 Bg6 19. Ne5 $14) 17. Nxe4 dxe4
