{[#]White seems to be stable but Black spotted his Achilee's heel. How?} 17...
Nb4 {[%csl Ra4] This simply wins the a4-pawn.} 18. Qd1 Bxe3 ({Of course not} 
18... Bxa4 $2 19. Bxa7 Rxa7 20. Rxe4) 19. Rxe3 Bxa4 $15 {Due to the blockade
on d4 White is far from losing, but in Zinn,L-Uhlmann,W Berlin East 1968 (0-1,
41) play remained one-sided.} *

